 <p><strong>Last reviewed:</strong> January 1, 2026</p>
 <p class="hero__lead">CoreFlow Specialty Infusion is committed to ensuring that coreflowrx.com is accessible to people with disabilities. We are working to conform to the Web Content Accessibility Guidelines (WCAG) 2.1, Level AA.</p>
